snippet: Kevin Dineen became the coach of Canada’s women’s hockey team for the Sochi Olympics, a month after his firing by the Florida Panthers.
lead_paragraph: Kevin Dineen became the coach of Canada’s women’s hockey team for the Sochi Olympics, a month after his firing by the Florida Panthers.
